  "title": "Heidelberg Q45",
  "body": "What does the resurrection of Christ profit us?\n\nFirst, by his resurrection he has overcome death, that he might make us partakers of that righteousness which he had purchased for us by his death. Secondly, we also are now by his power raised up to a new life. Thirdly, the resurrection of Christ is to us a sure pledge of our blessed resurrection.",
